snippet.title: Dungeon Hunter 3 - Official trailer by Gameloft
snippet.description:
iPhone / iPad - coming December 21st, 2011
Android - coming January 2012

The benchmark action/RPG series on the App Store is back in a third FREE installment, and it's even more legendary than ever!

Official site: http://www.gameloft.com
Friend us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Gameloft
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/Gameloft
Visit our blog: http://blog.gameloft.com
